type: web_research
title: Crypto Sentiment-Driven Trade Stop Signal System - Comprehensive Research
key_insights[19]: "Twitter/X API v2: Basic $200/mo, Pro $5000/mo. New pay-per-use pilot in closed beta (Nov 2025). Filtered Stream requires Basic tier minimum.","Apify Twitter Scraper: 1000+ tweets/min, no login needed, MCP support. Alternatives: Bright Data, snscrape (free OSS), twitterapi.io","CryptoPanic: News aggregator with API, MCP server available for AI agents (MIT license)","Whale Alert API: WebSocket at $29.95/mo (Custom Alerts), REST Enterprise at $699/mo. Supports 11 blockchains.","CryptoQuant: Free to $799/mo. Exchange flows, whale activity, miner behavior tracking.","Glassnode: Free to $799/mo. 1000+ assets, macro on-chain, NUPL/SSR proprietary indicators.","Arkham Intelligence: 300M+ address labels, 150K+ entity pages. AI engine 'Ultra' for real-time signals. KOL tracking launched Mar 2025.","CCXT: 106+ exchanges, WebSocket via CCXT Pro, funding rate/OI support. Funding rate timestamp inconsistencies between exchanges.","FinBERT (ProsusAI/finbert): Financial sentiment, 3 classes. CryptoBERT (ElKulako/cryptobert): 3.2M crypto posts, ~58.5% accuracy.","LLM cost optimization: Haiku $1/$5 per M tokens ideal for classification. Batch processing gives 50% discount. Prompt caching saves 90%.","Alternative.me Fear & Greed Index: Free API, 6 factors (volatility 25%, volume 25%, social 15%, dominance, trends 10%, surveys).","Freqtrade: 39.9K GitHub stars, FreqAI for ML integration, Docker deployment, Telegram control.","Jesse: 6.5K stars, 300+ indicators, JesseGPT assistant. VectorBT: Vectorized backtesting, custom indicator factory for sentiment.","ClickHouse: Best for analytics >100M rows/day, 10-30:1 compression. TimescaleDB: Best for relational+time-series, PostgreSQL ecosystem.","Kafka: Dominant for high-throughput crypto streaming. Redis Streams: Lightweight alternative. Combined architecture common.","Streamlit for rapid prototyping, Grafana+Prometheus for production monitoring, InfluxDB for time-series storage.","Token Metrics: AI price predictions. Nansen: Smart money tracking, 30+ chains. IntoTheBlock/Sentora: ML pattern detection.","TradingView webhooks: Pine Script v5, sub-100ms latency on premium, OAuth 2.0 security (2025 update).","Docker Compose standard for deployment. Freqtrade/Hummingbot Docker images available. AWS Lambda for serverless, Raspberry Pi for low-cost 24/7."
refs[13]: "Twitter API: https://developer.x.com/en/docs/x-api/filtered-stream-overview","CCXT: https://github.com/ccxt/ccxt","CryptoPanic API: https://cryptopanic.com/developers/api/","Whale Alert API: https://developer.whale-alert.io/documentation/","FinBERT: https://huggingface.co/ProsusAI/finbert","CryptoBERT: https://huggingface.co/ElKulako/cryptobert","Freqtrade: https://github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade","Jesse: https://github.com/jesse-ai/jesse","VectorBT: https://github.com/polakowo/vectorbt","Alternative.me API: https://alternative.me/crypto/api/","Arkham Intelligence: https://info.arkm.com/research","Glassnode: https://glassnode.com/products/data","CryptoQuant: https://cryptoquant.com"
recommendations[7]: Use Haiku/GPT-4o-mini for high-volume news classification with batch processing + prompt caching,Combine CryptoPanic (news) + Alternative.me (sentiment index) + Whale Alert (on-chain) for multi-source signals,"ClickHouse for historical analytics, TimescaleDB for transactional+time-series hybrid needs","Kafka for production event streaming, Redis Streams for lightweight/low-latency use cases","Freqtrade + FreqAI for backtesting with ML integration, VectorBT for rapid parameter optimization","Telegram Bot API with inline keyboards for signal delivery, Discord webhooks as secondary channel","Docker Compose for orchestration, VPS ($5-20/mo) or Raspberry Pi ($35-75 one-time) for low-cost deployment"
